              <span id="reviewTextContainer251447210" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7543350665259141283">I absolutely loved this book. I will be purchasing it for my library. I highly recommend it to all who want to know our Saviour more.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


